description:
Welcome to Tag Team Tuesdays. This is round 4 of 4 of the Live April matchup between The Ninjas and The Goddesses.
The wrestling is over and the winners are going to fuck the losers in front of the live audience. It's been a long time since Isis Love got fucked on the mat. It's even more fun when Vendetta makes her squirt in front of everybody!
title: FINAL ROUND
